          <p style="margin: 0 0 var(--s-3) 0; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: var(--text-md); font-weight: 500;">More <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;">Realtor partnership and borrower-side</a> resources at Stairway</p>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: var(--s-5); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.7; list-style: none;">
            <li>&rarr; <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/loan-programs/">All mortgage loan programs</a></li>
