<Layout title="Realtors · Florida Realtor Partner Hub — NAR Settlement, Buyer Agency Agreements &amp; Mortgage Coordination Specialist" description="Florida Realtor partner hub educating buyers and sellers on what licensed Realtors do in a real estate transaction post-NAR settlement effective August 17, 2024 (resolving Sitzer / Burnett class action for $418M settlement payment). Buyer's agents must execute written buyer agency agreement before showing property; listing brokers may no longer offer compensation on MLS platforms; cooperative compensation continues off-MLS through direct channels; buyer's agent commission remains negotiable per Redfin Q1 2025 data showing 2.40% average. Florida agency relationship types: transaction broker (default), single agent buyer or seller, designated sales associate (DSA), no-brokerage relationship. Realtor designations including CRS Certified Residential Specialist, ABR Accredited Buyer's Representative, GRI Graduate REALTOR Institute, SRES Seniors Real Estate Specialist, MRP Military Relocation Professional, RENE Real Estate Negotiation Expert, CIPS Certified International Property Specialist. Florida real estate law governing transaction broker default agency, single agent fiduciary duties (loyalty, confidentiality, obedience, full disclosure, accounting, skill care diligence), Designated Sales Associate dual representation. Top Florida brokerages including Compass, Coldwell Banker Realty, Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Florida Realty, RE/MAX, Keller Williams Realty, EXP Realty, Redfin, and luxury-tier Douglas Elliman, One Sotheby's International Realty, Premier Sotheby's, Engel and Volkers Florida, Christie's International Real Estate. Florida condo regulatory framework post-Surfside (SB 4-D May 2022, Structural Integrity Reserve Studies SIRS, milestone inspection requirements, reserve funding requirements). FIRPTA Foreign Investment in Real Property Tax Act withholding for foreign sellers. Realtor + mortgage lender coordination across 30-45 day Florida residential purchase transaction timeline: pre-approval, offer drafting and Florida Realtors / Florida Bar (FR/Bar) contract execution, contingency setup, inspection coordination, appraisal coordination, title and HOA estoppel, Closing Disclosure 3-day review under CFPB TRID rules, closing-day execution. Partner-as-borrower CTA at bottom routing Realtors looking for mortgages on their own home to dedicated Realtor-as-borrower mortgage guide with Schedule C 1099 commission income documentation under Fannie Mae B3-3.3-02 and Form 1084 cash-flow addback recovery." canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/realtors/">
  <div class="prealtor-scope" set:html={prealtorBody} />
</Layout>

<style is:global>
.prealtor-scope{
      color-scheme: light only;
      --ink: #0A0E1A;
      --ink-2: #1E2433;
      --ink-3: #2C3548;
      --ink-light: #4A5568;
      --ink-lighter: #6B7280;
      --paper: #FAFAF7;
      --paper-2: #F4F4EE;
      --paper-3: #EDEDE5;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --blue: #1845D6;
      --blue-deep: #0F2EA0;
      --blue-soft: #E8EEFF;
      --blue-tint: #F2F5FF;
      --gold: #B8860B;
      --rust: #8B2C2C;
      --border: #E5E5DE;
      --border-strong: #D4D4C8;
      --border-dark: #2C3548;
      --text-2xs: 0.6875rem; 
      --text-xs: 0.75rem;    
      --text-sm: 0.875rem;   
      --text-base: 1.0625rem;
      --text-md: 1.1875rem;  
      --text-lg: 1.375rem;   
      --text-xl: 1.625rem;   
      --text-2xl: 2rem;      
      --text-3xl: 2.75rem;   
      --text-4xl: 3.75rem;   
      --text-5xl: 5rem;      
      --s-1: 0.25rem;
      --s-2: 0.5rem;
      --s-3: 0.75rem;
      --s-4: 1rem;
      --s-5: 1.5rem;
      --s-6: 2rem;
      --s-7: 3rem;
      --s-8: 4rem;
      --s-9: 6rem;
      --s-10: 8rem;
      --s-11: 10rem;
      --serif: 'Fraunces', 'Iowan Old Style', Georgia, serif;
      --sans: 'IBM Plex Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', Menlo, monospace;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {.prealtor-scope, .prealtor-scope{
        background-color: #FAFAF7 !important;
        color: #0A0E1A !important;
        color-scheme: light only !important;
      }.prealtor-scope *{
        forced-color-adjust: none;
      }
    }.prealtor-scope, .prealtor-scope *::before, .prealtor-scope *::after{ box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }.prealtor-scope{ scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }.prealtor-scope{
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--paper);
      font-feature-settings: 'kern' 1, 'liga' 1, 'calt' 1;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }.prealtor-scope img, .prealtor-scope svg{ display: block; max-width: 100%; }.prealtor-scope a{ color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }.prealtor-scope button{ font: inherit; cursor: pointer; border: 0; background: none; }.prealtor-scope .container{ max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--s-6); }.prealtor-scope .container-narrow{ max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--s-6); }.prealtor-scope .container-wide{ max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--s-6); }.prealtor-scope .eyebrow{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 500;
      display: inline-block;
    }.prealtor-scope .display-1{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, var(--text-5xl));
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 30;
      color: var(--ink);
    }.prealtor-scope .display-2{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, var(--text-3xl));
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 100, "SOFT" 50;
      color: var(--ink);
    }.prealtor-scope h2{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, var(--text-2xl));
      font-weight: 450;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.015em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 60, "SOFT" 50;
    }.prealtor-scope h3{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30;
    }.prealtor-scope h4{
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: var(--text-md);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
      letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    }.prealtor-scope p{ margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }.prealtor-scope p:last-child{ margin-bottom: 0; }.prealtor-scope p.lead{
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      font-weight: 350;
    }.prealtor-scope p.lede{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 350;
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30;
    }.prealtor-scope .body-text{ color: var(--ink-2); }.prealtor-scope .text-muted{ color: var(--ink-lighter); }.prealtor-scope .text-small{ font-size: var(--text-sm); }.prealtor-scope .text-mono{ font-family: var(--mono); font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1; }.prealtor-scope strong, .prealtor-scope b{ font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }.prealtor-scope em, .prealtor-scope i{ font-style: italic; }.prealtor-scope .nav{
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }.prealtor-scope .nav-inner{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-6);
      max-width: 1340px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }.prealtor-scope .logo{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--s-3);
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: var(--text-md);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30;
    }.prealtor-scope .logo-mark{
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      background: var(--ink);
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }.prealtor-scope .logo-mark::before{
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 5px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--white);
      border-right: 2px solid var(--white);
    }.prealtor-scope .logo-mark::after{
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 5px 9px 9px 5px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--white);
      border-right: 2px solid var(--white);
    }.prealtor-scope .logo-sub{ font-size: var(--text-2xs); color: var(--ink-lighter); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }.prealtor-scope .nav-links{
      display: flex; gap: var(--s-6); list-style: none;
      font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 500;
    }.prealtor-scope .nav-links a{ color: var(--ink-2); transition: color 0.15s; }.prealtor-scope .nav-links a:hover{ color: var(--blue); }.prealtor-scope .nav-cta{
      display: flex; gap: var(--s-3);
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {.prealtor-scope .nav-links{ display: none; }.prealtor-scope .nav-cta .btn-secondary{ display: none; }
    }.prealtor-scope .btn{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--s-2);
      padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.005em;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: all 0.18s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-primary{
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-primary:hover{
      background: var(--blue);
      border-color: var(--blue);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-secondary{
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-secondary:hover{
      border-color: var(--ink);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-light{
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-light:hover{ background: var(--paper-2); }.prealtor-scope .btn-large{
      padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-6);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-arrow{
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--s-2);
      color: var(--blue); font-weight: 500;
      transition: gap 0.18s;
    }.prealtor-scope .btn-arrow:hover{ gap: var(--s-3); }.prealtor-scope .btn-arrow::after{ content: '→'; font-family: var(--sans); }.prealtor-scope .hero{
      padding: var(--s-9) 0 var(--s-8);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }.prealtor-scope .breadcrumb{
      display: flex; gap: var(--s-2);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--ink-lighter);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-7);
    }.prealtor-scope .breadcrumb a{ color: var(--ink-lighter); }.prealtor-scope .breadcrumb a:hover{ color: var(--blue); }.prealtor-scope .breadcrumb span:last-child{ color: var(--ink); }.prealtor-scope .hero-eyebrow{ margin-bottom: var(--s-5); }.prealtor-scope .hero h1{ margin-bottom: var(--s-6); max-width: 18ch; }.prealtor-scope .hero-subtitle{
      max-width: 56ch;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-7);
    }.prealtor-scope .hero-actions{
      display: flex; gap: var(--s-3);
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
    }.prealtor-scope .hero-trust{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      color: var(--ink-lighter);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--s-3);
    }.prealtor-scope .trust-dot{ width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--blue); }.prealtor-scope .stats{
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      padding: var(--s-7) 0;
    }.prealtor-scope .stats-grid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: var(--s-5);
    }.prealtor-scope .stat{
      padding: 0 var(--s-4);
      border-left: 1px solid var(--ink-3);
    }.prealtor-scope .stat:first-child{ border-left: 0; padding-left: 0; }.prealtor-scope .stat-num{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.2vw, 2.6rem); overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      font-weight: 350;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
    }.prealtor-scope .stat-label{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {.prealtor-scope .stats-grid{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--s-7) var(--s-4); }.prealtor-scope .stat:nth-child(3){ border-left: 0; padding-left: 0; }
    }.prealtor-scope .section{
      padding: var(--s-10) 0;
    }.prealtor-scope .section-tinted{ background: var(--paper-2); }.prealtor-scope .section-dark{ background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }.prealtor-scope .section-header{
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
    }.prealtor-scope .section-header .eyebrow{ margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }.prealtor-scope .section-header h2{ margin-bottom: var(--s-5); }.prealtor-scope .section-header p{ font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--ink-2); }.prealtor-scope .lede-section{ padding: var(--s-9) 0; }.prealtor-scope .lede-section .lede + .lede{ margin-top: var(--s-5); }.prealtor-scope .data-table{
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    }.prealtor-scope .data-table thead th{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink-lighter);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: left;
      padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-4);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td{
      padding: var(--s-5) var(--s-4);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      vertical-align: top;
    }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody tr:hover{ background: rgba(24, 69, 214, 0.025); }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td:first-child{
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      width: 28%;
    }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td:nth-child(2){
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      color: var(--blue-deep);
      white-space: nowrap;
      width: 28%;
    }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td:last-child{
      color: var(--ink-2);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {.prealtor-scope .data-table thead{ display: none; }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody tr{
        display: block;
        padding: var(--s-5) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td{
        display: block;
        padding: 0 0 var(--s-2);
        border: 0;
        width: 100% !important;
      }.prealtor-scope .data-table tbody td:first-child{ font-size: var(--text-md); }
    }.prealtor-scope .methods-intro{ max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: var(--s-8); }.prealtor-scope .methods-grid{
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--s-5);
    }.prealtor-scope .method{
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: var(--s-7);
      position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
    }.prealtor-scope .method:hover{
      border-color: var(--border-strong);
    }.prealtor-scope .method-header{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: var(--s-5);
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-5);
    }.prealtor-scope .method-num{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--blue);
      line-height: 1;
      padding-top: var(--s-2);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }.prealtor-scope .method-title h3{
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      line-height: 1.15;
    }.prealtor-scope .method-tag{
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      padding: var(--s-1) var(--s-3);
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue-deep);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
    }.prealtor-scope .method-body{
      padding-left: calc(var(--text-2xl) + var(--s-5));
    }.prealtor-scope .method-body > p{ margin-bottom: var(--s-5); color: var(--ink-2); }.prealtor-scope .worked-example{
      background: var(--paper-2);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--ink);
      padding: var(--s-5) var(--s-6);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      line-height: 1.7;
      border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured{
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border-left-color: var(--blue);
    }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured .we-label{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured .we-result{ color: var(--paper); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured .we-num{ color: var(--paper); }.prealtor-scope .we-title{
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
      color: var(--ink);
    }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured .we-title{ color: var(--blue-soft); }.prealtor-scope .we-line{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: var(--s-4);
      padding: var(--s-2) 0;
    }.prealtor-scope .we-label{ color: var(--ink-light); }.prealtor-scope .we-num{ color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }.prealtor-scope .we-divider{
      border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-strong);
      margin: var(--s-3) 0;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }.prealtor-scope .worked-example.featured .we-divider{ border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }.prealtor-scope .we-result{
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      padding-top: var(--s-3);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      margin-top: var(--s-2);
      font-weight: 600;
    }.prealtor-scope .we-result .we-label{ color: var(--ink); }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {.prealtor-scope .method{ padding: var(--s-5); }.prealtor-scope .method-body{ padding-left: 0; }.prealtor-scope .method-num{ font-size: var(--text-xl); }
    }.prealtor-scope .callout{
      background: var(--blue-tint);
      border: 1px solid rgba(24, 69, 214, 0.12);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: var(--s-6) var(--s-7);
      max-width: 760px;
    }.prealtor-scope .callout-eyebrow{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
    }.prealtor-scope .callout p{
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 350;
      font-variation-settings: "opsz" 30;
    }.prealtor-scope .testim-warning{
      background: #FFF1F1;
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 44, 44, 0.3);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
      text-align: center;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      color: var(--rust);
      margin: 0 auto var(--s-7);
      max-width: 800px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--s-3);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }.prealtor-scope .testim-warning .mono-tag{
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: var(--text-2xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      background: var(--rust);
      color: var(--paper);
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 600;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }.prealtor-scope .testimonials-grid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--s-5);
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {.prealtor-scope .testimonials-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s-6); max-width: 620px; }
    }.prealtor-scope .testimonials-grid--quad{
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      max-width: 1100px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {.prealtor-scope .testimonials-grid--quad{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 620px; }
    }.prealtor-scope .testim-card{
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: var(--s-6);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--s-5);
      position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
    }.prealtor-scope .testim-card:hover{
